reviewText: I like it and have been working with a few students on Randall's book "The Partial Capo" and this video, which, I have to say, bears multiple viewings due to the unavoidable complexities of music theory.  I'm glad I bought "Partial Capo Techniques with Randall Williams" and I'm sure there's a lot of treasure to be found in getting more familiar with its' many possibilities.
